---
/**
 * Slide 01 v2 · Cover. Editorial / serif-driven.
 * Inspired by Reach's purple-midnight + orange-saccharine + Playfair feel.
 * Tailwind built-in tokens only.
 */
const id = 'apprenticeship-degree';
---

<section id={id} class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-16 bg-stone-50 dark:bg-indigo-950 vibrant:bg-black snap-start">
  <span class="absolute top-6 right-8 text-xs tracking-widest font-mono text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 vibrant:text-orange-500">01 / 09</span>

  <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 vibrant:text-orange-500 mb-8">
    Reach University · The Apprenticeship Degree
  </p>

  <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl text-indigo-950 dark:text-stone-50 vibrant:text-stone-50 leading-[1.04] tracking-tight max-w-5xl mb-10">
    Turn your job <em class="not-italic text-orange-500">into a degree.</em>
  </h1>

  <p class="font-serif italic text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-cyan-300 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed mb-16">
    A fully accredited college degree where the workplace is the classroom — roughly half the learning happens through on-the-job work, the rest through after-hours seminars.
  </p>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-0 max-w-4xl border-y border-indigo-950/20 dark:border-stone-50/20 vibrant:border-orange-500/40">
    <div class="p-6 md:border-r border-b md:border-b-0 border-indigo-950/20 dark:border-stone-50/20 vibrant:border-orange-500/40">
      <p class="font-serif text-5xl text-orange-500 mb-1">A</p>
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 vibrant:text-cyan-300 mb-3">Affordable</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-50/80 font-serif italic leading-snug">Earn a paycheck while earning the degree.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 md:border-r border-b md:border-b-0 border-indigo-950/20 dark:border-stone-50/20 vibrant:border-orange-500/40">
      <p class="font-serif text-5xl text-orange-500 mb-1">B</p>
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 vibrant:text-cyan-300 mb-3">Based in the workplace</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-50/80 font-serif italic leading-snug">The workplace transforms into a learning place.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6">
      <p class="font-serif text-5xl text-orange-500 mb-1">C</p>
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 vibrant:text-cyan-300 mb-3">Credit for what you do</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-50/80 font-serif italic leading-snug">Real, fully accredited — not a certificate.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-12 max-w-3xl font-serif text-base text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-400 vibrant:text-cyan-300/80 leading-relaxed">
    Sector goal: <span class="font-semibold text-indigo-950 dark:text-stone-50 vibrant:text-orange-500">3 million Apprenticeship Degree completions by 2035</span> — driven by the National Center for the Apprenticeship Degree (NCAD), launched 2024.
  </p>
</section>
